Homepage: https://github.com/maranode/maranode
Description: Private, air-gapped AI inference runtime
 Maranode runs large language models entirely on-premises.
 No data leaves the machine. Includes a REST API compatible
 with the OpenAI chat completions format, a web UI, RAG
 support, and a tamper-evident audit log.
